"The Cabinet, Cabinet committees and technical committees will not have any scheduled engagements unless directed by President Uhuru Kenyatta, for urgent business, cases of national emergency or any other exceptional circumstances," he said.
Cabinet members excluding those in the NSC and the National Emergency Response Committee on Coronavirus will be allowed to take leave, subject to the President's approval.



